data.description: Delightful is a perfect way to describe this ranch home in the desirable Anchor Park Neighborhood. The bright and cheerful living spaces have been updated throughout to include paint, carpet, lighting, windows and bathroom. Featuring 3 bedrooms, large dining area and gas fireplace. Outside, the fully fenced backyard with shed offers multiple seating areas forenjoying Alaska's delightful summers while mature trees afford you privacy and serenity . Just minutes from the coveted Fire Island Bakery and Chester Creek trail system, UAA and the UMED district, this lovely home offers inspiring spaces for enjoyment outside and in, whatever the season or weather. Come home to 2649 Lake Otis Pkwy.
